{
  "type": "excalidraw",
  "version": 2,
  "source": "https://excalidraw.com",
  "elements": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100, "y": 10,
      "width": 700, "height": 36,
      "text": "Last-Token Pooling vs Mean Pooling for Decoder-Only LLMs",
      "fontSize": 20, "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "mean_box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 30, "y": 60,
      "width": 380, "height": 260,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131", "backgroundColor": "#fff5f5",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 2, "roundness": {"type": 3}
    },
    {
      "id": "mean_title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 40, "y": 72,
      "width": 360, "height": 28,
      "text": "Mean Pooling  ❌ (wrong for causal LMs)",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#e03131", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "mean_tokens",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 44, "y": 110,
      "width": 360, "height": 200,
      "text": "Tokens: [PAD] [PAD] \"Hello\" \"world\" \"!\"\n\nCausal attention: each token only attends\nto itself and prior tokens.\n\n\"Hello\" → attends to [Hello]\n\"world\" → attends to [Hello, world]\n  \"!\"   → attends to [Hello, world, !]\n\nMean-pooling averages ALL positions,\nincluding [PAD] (masked out) and early\ntokens that have partial context.\n\n→ Representation is diluted and inconsistent",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "last_box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 490, "y": 60,
      "width": 380, "height": 260,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44", "backgroundColor": "#f0fff4",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 5, "roundness": {"type": 3}
    },
    {
      "id": "last_title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 500, "y": 72,
      "width": 360, "height": 28,
      "text": "Last-Token Pooling  ✓ (correct for causal LMs)",
      "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "last_tokens",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 502, "y": 110,
      "width": 360, "height": 200,
      "text": "Tokens: [PAD] [PAD] \"Hello\" \"world\" \"!\"\n                                          ↑\n                                   z = h[-1]\n\nWith left-padding (padding_side='left'):\nthe LAST position is always the last real\ncontent token, regardless of padding.\n\n\"!\" has attended to the full sequence:\n  [Hello, world, !] → complete context\n\nThis is how GTE-Qwen, LLM2Vec, and\nE5-Mistral all extract representations.\n\n→ Single vector with full-sequence context",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "vs_label",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 430, "y": 170,
      "width": 50, "height": 40,
      "text": "VS",
      "fontSize": 20, "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#7950f2", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "impl_box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 30, "y": 360,
      "width": 840, "height": 90,
      "strokeColor": "#7950f2", "backgroundColor": "#f8f0ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 9, "roundness": {"type": 3}
    },
    {
      "id": "impl_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 44, "y": 374,
      "width": 810, "height": 65,
      "text": "Implementation (3 lines):\n\ndef last_token_pool(hidden_states, attention_mask):\n    return hidden_states[:, -1, :]   # With left-padding, position -1 is always last real token",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0, "seed": 10
    }
  ],
  "appState": {
    "viewBackgroundColor": "#ffffff",
    "currentItemFontFamily": 1
  },
  "files": {}
}
